Package io.spine.server.model.declare

This package defines of the declaration requirements of Entity API methods, that are typically created by the framework end-user.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    ParameterSpec<E extends io.spine.core.MessageEnvelope<?,?,?>>
    A specification of handler method parameters, specific for various HandlerMethod implementations.

    Enum Description
    MatchCriterion

    Thrown for handler method in case its wrapped method does not match method signature, set for the handler.
